ights, sounds, and spirit of India. Every street corner holds a potential lead, a valuable item, or an unexpected encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450840/extras/4f47b9f6a2b9beac451d09b93e4eb4bb.avif?t=1751374640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450840/extras_big/4f47b9f6a2b9beac451d09b93e4eb4bb.avif?t=1751374640 width=800 height=147 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Barter, bargain, and buy your way to the truth.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nothing comes easy in Dotson’s world — you’ll need to haggle like a pro to get what you need. Buy incense sticks, street food, Bollywood memorabilia and more, and trade them smartly to open up new conversations, gather intel, and move closer to solving each case.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450840/extras/cf9e83afdeec6f8c1e94502df3313923.avif?t=1751374640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450840/extras_big/cf9e83afdeec6f8c1e94502df3313923.avif?t=1751374640 width=800 height=115 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play mini-games and earn your keep.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into fun mini-games scattered around the city, including street cricket and Bollywood dance-offs. Winning games means better bargaining power — and sometimes, vital clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450840/extras/163027b2a9fa5ef6256e1d4f9f2374a5.avif?t=1751374640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450840/extras_big/163027b2a9fa5ef6256e1d4f9f2374a5.avif?t=1751374640 width=800 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meet an unforgettable cast.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From mischievous shopkeepers to notorious gangsters, the city is full of colorful characters waiting to help (or hinder) Detective Dotson. Charm them, outwit them, or catch them red-handed — how you interact can change the outcome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450840/extras/343bd9b339f1774b49288aca932e888a.avif?t=1751374640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450840/extras_big/343bd9b339f1774b49288aca932e888a.avif?t=1751374640 width=800 height=141 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A mystery with heart (and a lot of samosas).</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you crack each case, a deeper, more personal story begins to unfold — one connected to Detective Dotson himself. Expect surprises, laughs, and a love letter to the rich culture and chaotic charm of India.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450840/extras/66c9fda47bc6739e41fae1ca1271048a.avif?t=1751374640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450840/extras_big/66c9fda47bc6739e41fae1ca1271048a.avif?t=1751374640 width=800 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
